      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_backstage-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……いい話なのは、確かなんだけど\nこの仕事、やっぱり私には合わないわ",
      "startTime": 3.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロには私よりふさわしい子達がいるでしょう？\n彼女達に頼んだ方が……",
      "startTime": 11.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "先方が莉央さんにぜひ頼みたいそうなんです",
      "startTime": 13.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今までにない花嫁像を表現して顧客拡大に繋げたい\n莉央さんとなら、それが出来ると",
      "startTime": 20.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "でもブライダルのテレビCMでしょ？\nウエディングドレスを着て、にっこり笑う感じよね？",
      "startTime": 26.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "そういうのを否定する訳じゃないけど……\n私のイメージだと、似合わないんじゃない？",
      "startTime": 33.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、クールでかっこいい花嫁を表現したいから\n莉央さんの凛とした雰囲気がぴったりなんだそうです",
      "startTime": 40.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "先方のプロデューサーは\n莉央さん以外に考えられない、と言っています",
      "startTime": 45.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方、随分熱心にこの仕事を勧めるわね\nいつもなら、本人の意向が一番です、って言うじゃない",
      "startTime": 53.4955797791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "も、もちろん莉央さんの意向が一番ですよ！\n特に、その……他意はないです！",
      "startTime": 61.3333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり今日の{user}さん、何か変よ\n……あ、そろそろ時間だわ。ライブ会場に行かないと",
      "startTime": 68.7666669209,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11100.00000000001,
          "startTime": 79.8666669209
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "この件だけど、あまり期待はしないでちょうだい\n自分が納得出来ない仕事は、したくないから",
      "startTime": 76.4333381652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（出来れば、やってほしいんだけどな……）\n（莉央さんのためにも）",
      "startTime": 85.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3266.6673025999985,
          "startTime": 88.6000006359
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3533.34274289999,
          "startTime": 88.8666760762
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します。ライブ、大成功でしたね\nって、あれ、莉央さんだけ……？",
      "startTime": 93.3145209887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "屈辱だわ！！",
      "startTime": 96.8000006359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ！？　ど、どうしました？\nライブ、凄く良かったのに",
      "startTime": 101.0322594215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "ライブの出来じゃないわよ！\nさっき、こころにこのネットニュースを見せられたの！",
      "startTime": 105.5333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、その記事は……\n『お嫁さんにしたいアイドルランキング』……",
      "startTime": 112.5279345066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "一位は遙子\n理由。家庭的な感じ。優しそう。癒される……",
      "startTime": 117.1390428432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "これは分かるわ。イメージにぴったりだし\n私だって彼女に投票するわよ。だけど……",
      "startTime": 123.9666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "私はランキング圏内ギリギリの三十位……\nしかも理由は、もの凄く気が強そうだけど料理上手",
      "startTime": 131.4666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "自分にも厳しいけど、夫にはもっと厳しそう\n規則正しく生きられそうだけど、家庭には笑顔もほしい",
      "startTime": 140.2999987285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……どのコメントも、一言余計なのよ！！\n私に投票しておいて、なんなの！？",
      "startTime": 147.7333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁ、ランキングには入ったんですから……",
      "startTime": 150.3666647594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "でも最下位だったのよ！\nLizNoirの中で！！",
      "startTime": 155.8333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "愛は、見たことないくらい汗をかきながら\n必死にフォローしてくるし",
      "startTime": 160.0666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "葵には「花嫁がダメなら花婿になればいい」って\n言われたわ。……私、ひょっとして慰められたの？",
      "startTime": 165.6333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "こころには「あれ～？　莉央さんセンターなのに\nこころより下なんですねぇ～？」",
      "startTime": 173.9999987285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "「もしかして、初めての敗北味わっちゃいました？」\nって煽られるし……私のプライドはズタズタよ！",
      "startTime": 180.7195270323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "あげくに、みんな私のこと腫れ物扱いして\n荷物をまとめてそそくさと帰って行ったのよ！",
      "startTime": 188.8333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "り、莉央さん、落ち着いて下さい！\nこんなのは一部のファンの遊びみたいなもので……",
